## Components
- sensors / input devices:
Humidity Sensor, Flow sensor
- processing node:
Ubuntu server probably using a vps
- communication
MQTT, Twingate for pi access
- storage
IfluxDB
- dashboard / app
Grafana
- actuators / notifications
Using Grafana contact point we can send an email notification to multiple users.

